OL,3,CWho is top Tory donor at centre of
OL,4,CDiane Abbott racism row?
OL,6,FHe is the Conservative Party's biggest
OL,7,Fdonor, has rubbed shoulders with the
OL,8,Flikes of David Cameron and Boris
OL,9,FJohnson and has built a business worth
OL,10,Fan estimated #1bn.
OL,12,FLabour Party leader Sir Keir Starmer
OL,13,Fcalled him the man "bankrolling" the
OL,14,Fcurrent Prime Minister Rishi Sunak.
OL,16,FBut until recently, Frank Hester's
OL,17,Fprofile remained relatively low.
OL,19,FThat all changed when comments he
OL,20,Fallegedly made about MP Diane Abbott
OL,21,Fwere reported by a national newspaper.
