OL,6,FSo, who is Frank Hester and how did he
OL,7,Ffind himself at the centre of a
OL,8,Fpolitical storm?
OL,10,FThe son of Irish immigrants who
OL,11,Ftrained to be a priest
OL,13,FOne of five siblings, Hester, 57, grew
OL,14,Fup in Armley, a deprived suburb of
OL,15,FLeeds.
OL,17,FPosting on X, he said his parents met
OL,18,Fin the city ` his father had emigrated
OL,19,Fafter "building hay sheds on farms in
OL,20,FIreland". His mother had also moved
OL,21,Ffrom Ireland.
