OL,6,FThey started a plastering business,
OL,7,Fwhich itself became a million-pound
OL,8,Fenterprise.
OL,10,FHester said his mother, who was in
OL,11,Fcharge of payroll, "inspired me to
OL,12,Fwrite code".
OL,14,FHe wrote computer software which
OL,15,Fenabled her to complete her tasks more
OL,16,Fquickly and went on to develop a
OL,17,Fcareer as a software architect.
OL,19,FBut, before going to university to
OL,20,Fstudy computer science, Hester trained
OL,21,Fto be a priest.
