OL,6,FAccording to The Guardian, Mr Hester
OL,7,Fmade remarks about Hackney MP Ms
OL,8,FAbbott in 2019 during a meeting at
OL,9,FTPP's Leeds headquarters.
OL,11,FThe newspaper reported that he said:
OL,12,F"It's like trying not to be racist but
OL,13,Fyou see Diane Abbott on the TV, and
OL,14,Fyou're just like... you just want to
OL,15,Fhate all black women because she's
OL,16,Fthere.
OL,18,F"And I don't hate all black women at
OL,19,Fall, but I think she should be shot."
