OL,6,FHow has Frank Hester responded and
OL,7,Fwhat has been the wider reaction?
OL,9,FA statement released on Hester's X
OL,10,Faccount on 11 March said he "accepts
OL,11,Fthat he was rude about Diane Abbot in
OL,12,Fa private meeting several years ago",
OL,13,Fbut added his criticism had "nothing
OL,14,Fto do with her gender nor colour of
OL,15,Fskin".
OL,17,FThe statement added: "The Guardian is
OL,18,Fright when it quotes Frank saying he
OL,19,Fabhors racism, not least because he
OL,20,Fexperienced it as the child of Irish
OL,21,Fimmigrants in the 1970s.
