OL,7,Ftry to apologise directly for the hurt
OL,8,Fhe has caused her, and is deeply sorry
OL,9,Ffor his remarks. He wishes to make it
OL,10,Fclear that he regards racism as a
OL,11,Fpoison which has no place in public
OL,12,Flife."
OL,14,FIn a follow-up post he added: "The UK
OL,15,Fbenefits immensely from the rich
